Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.20,0:01:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绫女来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.84,0:01:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呵呵…不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.78,0:01:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以前曾经出场过一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.58,0:01:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是负责打理草摩温泉旅馆的老板娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.05,0:01:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呵呵…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.35,0:01:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天工作人员硬是拜托我来介绍一下绫女少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.53,0:01:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我只好忍辱出场了 呵呵…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.83,0:01:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思 请各位见谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.07,0:01:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶？虾咪咚咚？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.50,0:02:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦…已经开始啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.57,0:02:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么！真的啊？哎呀 这下怎么办…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.24,0:02:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,旁白的原稿呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.85,0:02:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕 原稿乱七八糟…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.88,0:02:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绫女少爷是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.28,0:02:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀 念得太慢 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.42,0:02:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是家里的长子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.32,0:02:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这下子有介绍跟没介绍一样 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.26,0:02:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,电视台的大人 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.96,0:02:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在客厅的各位观众 对…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.33,0:02:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好棒耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.46,0:02:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.83,0:02:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别怀疑 由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.00,0:02:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的我也准备好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.37,0:02:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托你的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.27,0:02:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在的店变得比以前还要出色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.84,0:02:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然世界这么大 但没有一间店比本店…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.61,0:02:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好想去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.52,0:02:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你刚才说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.92,0:02:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很想亲眼看看那间店到底有多棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.46,0:02:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有没有听到 紫吴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.53,0:02:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希耶 那个由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.20,0:03:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然眼中泛着泪光求我让他到我店里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.13,0:03:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.90,0:03:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有比这个更棒的吗 没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.34,0:03:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然不能不理会啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.04,0:03:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你听到了吗 波鸟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.04,0:03:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希 那个由希…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.41,0:03:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.28,0:03:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我实感光荣 欢迎之至
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.51,0:03:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个礼拜天请务必莅临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.15,0:03:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透 你也要一起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.58,0:03:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,公主一定要随时陪着王子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.59,0:03:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.65,0:03:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过你就不必来了 阿夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.76,0:03:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.39,0:03:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎么好像很不服气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.09,0:03:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 那就破例让你来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.73,0:03:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滚出去 变态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.63,0:03:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了 由希竟然会主动想接近绫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.24,0:03:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过他脸色好像不太好看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.01,0:03:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关于我哥哥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.17,0:03:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.14,0:03:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今后要一点一点地…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.14,0:03:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.51,0:03:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一点一点地去了解他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.08,0:03:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己要一点一点地去了解他才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.66,0:03:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.96,0:04:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能陪我去吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.03,0:04:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来由希已经有相当觉悟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.30,0:04:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧 就让我来帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.34,0:04:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的 只要不会妨碍你 就请让我一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.47,0:04:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.84,0:04:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪里 我以前就常想去看看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.38,0:04:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前泼春曾告诉我说那是间在卖"护士"、"空姐"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.68,0:04:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"女仆"等服装的店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.85,0:04:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,护士？女仆？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.99,0:04:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.26,0:04:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望别让他误解更深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.50,0:04:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就这样 下个礼拜天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.00,0:04:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我本田透就要陪着由希一起去拜访绫女的店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.31,0:04:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像就是这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.88,0:04:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.45,0:04:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,招牌的设计相当有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.95,0:05:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那招牌上可疑的设计引发我内心新的不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.16,0:05:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手工艺店？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.29,0:05:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天本店休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.90,0:05:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美音 这下摆的摺边…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.34,0:05:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.98,0:05:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我感觉到有东西跑过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.41,0:05:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是个来历不明的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.92,0:05:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.15,0:05:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我正在处理客人订的婚纱的下摆摺边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.69,0:05:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男人的尺寸合适吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.46,0:05:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然合适 订的人就是男的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.39,0:05:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是男人要穿的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.10,0:05:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每个人都会有一两个或三个不可告人的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.70,0:05:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这间到底是什么店？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.81,0:05:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相当简单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.61,0:06:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像想买手艺品的客人一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.45,0:06:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想要订做服装的客人也可以到我们店来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.08,0:06:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然啦 客人所订的服装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.95,0:06:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是由我这个老板亲手缝制的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.32,0:06:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管是什么样的设计都难不倒我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.56,0:06:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这只是完成的样品中的一小部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.26,0:06:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇 泼春说的就是这个啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.40,0:06:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了…绫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.03,0:06:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 我真的很棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.33,0:06:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎样 由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.97,0:06:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也可以坦率的说出你对我的赞赏之词啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.07,0:06:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么都是这种服装？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.54,0:06:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为是人气商品啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.74,0:06:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最畅销的是女仆服装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.21,0:06:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人气商品？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.31,0:06:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的！或许由希你还很难懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.15,0:06:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过这些就是男人的浪漫！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.15,0:06:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女仆、护士、女服务生、空姐、秘书、女医生、老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.62,0:06:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女高中生、女警、律师、电梯女郎、百货公司女郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.62,0:06:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猫耳、兔子耳、豹耳 我实在无法全部说完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.96,0:06:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男人们驰骋于这些梦想中寻找着自己的浪漫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.66,0:06:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在现实当中追梦 这不是一种罪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.37,0:07:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渴望偷窥女性入浴也是一种浪漫啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.54,0:07:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是犯罪行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.31,0:07:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们好像聊得很开心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.54,0:07:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他突然说今天要休息 我还以为是什么事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.98,0:07:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来是他弟弟要来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.92,0:07:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外表长得和店长一模一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.66,0:07:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初次见面您好 弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.56,0:07:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫做仓前美音 是员工之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.26,0:07:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也有参与服装制作喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.86,0:07:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.03,0:07:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么那件是店里的制服吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.07,0:07:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是 这是我喜欢的 很可爱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.87,0:07:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.77,0:07:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我今天是打扮成女仆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.21,0:07:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过我会照每天的心情来换穿不同的服装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.35,0:07:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美音戴着眼镜的样子深获店里男性客人的好评
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.72,0:07:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你觉得如何 由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.95,0:07:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希 你觉得戴眼镜的女孩如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.39,0:07:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戴眼镜的女孩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.72,0:07:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多人都有戴眼镜 一点都不稀奇了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.43,0:07:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等 他的表情可不是这么说的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.96,0:07:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错 由希 眼镜 美少女就要配眼镜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.06,0:08:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是从昭和就一直脉脉相传的男人浪漫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.93,0:08:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昭和的浪漫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.37,0:08:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是由历史来证明有意义的服装啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.34,0:08:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他还有什么服装？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.41,0:08:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么服装？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.58,0:08:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我什么都穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.61,0:08:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基本上我没有讨厌的服装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.98,0:08:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过与其穿水手服 我比较喜欢短夹克配格子百摺裙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.32,0:08:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且我不喜欢大象袜 比较喜欢深蓝长统袜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.12,0:08:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,护士服的话我不喜欢白色或粉红色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.05,0:08:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比较喜欢浅蓝和草绿色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.16,0:08:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,类似齿科护士那种清爽的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.32,0:08:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且不要戴护士帽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.89,0:08:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空姐服装的话我比较喜欢XX航空的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.70,0:08:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而不是最有名的XX航空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.06,0:08:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 女服务生的服装则是XXX的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.43,0:08:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有这个我是服从多数的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.87,0:08:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这件衣服可爱的摺边已经精心设计的围裙式样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.44,0:08:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,实在叫人爱不释手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.97,0:08:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过仔细想想 既然穿什么衣服都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.41,0:08:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那当然就要很讲究罗 我这个人应该挺挑剔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.21,0:08:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好 你的这个讲究支持着日本的传统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.02,0:08:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并创造出更美好的明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.35,0:08:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他夸我了 店长夸我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.65,0:08:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夸你了 我夸店员了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.22,0:09:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 护士还是白的最好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.19,0:09:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.19,0:09:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说XX航空比XX航空的好 我觉得你的选择很对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.43,0:09:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果能再更进一步到XXX那就更完美了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.50,0:09:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,XXX的领子我不喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.44,0:09:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个领子才是重点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.47,0:09:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感觉上很禁欲主义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.51,0:09:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也崇拜禁欲主义啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.31,0:09:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过那个领子和围巾与其说是禁欲倒不如…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.11,0:09:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要告诉你一件事 大象袜和深蓝长统袜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.68,0:09:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并不是袜子的全部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.12,0:09:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想像一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.08,0:09:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果穿着一双纯白到小腿肚中间的短袜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.36,0:09:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,店长 你太古板了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.96,0:09:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.06,0:09:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,学到旧的才知道新的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.59,0:09:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管什么时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.93,0:09:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要忘记"温故知新"这是比什么都重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.30,0:09:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 店长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.50,0:09:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.17,0:09:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 我从刚才就一直想问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.47,0:09:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那位女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.91,0:09:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好 我叫本田透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.05,0:09:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透小姐 你喜欢这类的服装？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.35,0:10:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想穿穿看吗？不想吗？应该想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.28,0:10:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她好像又开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.55,0:10:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来换衣服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.36,0:10:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美音一看到可爱的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.29,0:10:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就会想要让她换穿不同的服装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.46,0:10:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 仓前小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.63,0:10:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弟弟 你希望小透穿什么样的服装？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.70,0:10:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我比较倾向较整洁的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.04,0:10:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜欢…不是啦 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.74,0:10:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美音 我看还是那个最棒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.87,0:10:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个吗 老板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.21,0:10:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.04,0:10:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个实在很有魅力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.71,0:10:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.85,0:10:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来吧 小透小姐 请期待她变成那样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.12,0:10:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她并不是要拘禁小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.66,0:10:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毕竟美音也是个人 不会把她抓去吃掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.36,0:10:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个到底是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.33,0:10:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是老板娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.77,0:10:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才一开始我乱了阵脚 实在是很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.24,0:10:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我忍辱再度出场了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.11,0:11:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实本周阿夹的戏份超少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.42,0:11:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以工作人员就说 来开辟个"阿夹精选集"吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.52,0:11:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然这样 就把以前所有关于夹的精彩镜头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.86,0:11:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由我来用VTR编辑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.53,0:11:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让大家能多看到阿夹的酷样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.93,0:11:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是很诚心在做这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.37,0:11:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 哪有我的酷样镜头啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.60,0:11:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呵呵呵呵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.14,0:11:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呵呵什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.47,0:11:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且这边都是你的镜头啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.58,0:11:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起！我会重作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.41,0:11:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会重新作个我的镜头较少的VTR
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.82,0:11:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.02,0:11:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我就说不需要老板娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.95,0:11:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水手服～水手服～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.89,0:11:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,饭团星人穿水手服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.23,0:11:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样可以了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.97,0:12:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么一来就能让他们兄弟俩单独聊聊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.94,0:12:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许是我鸡婆 但难得有这个机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.01,0:12:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你愿意帮我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.01,0:12:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.01,0:12:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.09,0:12:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望他们能好好谈 不要再吵架了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.16,0:12:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵架更好 那就表示更了解对方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.29,0:12:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,店长最害怕的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.16,0:12:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫过于"无"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.30,0:12:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过我希望他们俩别打到流血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.54,0:12:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,万一血沾到商品上面那就伤脑筋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.75,0:12:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就因为他们互相了解对方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.28,0:12:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才会打架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.79,0:12:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过我们这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.56,0:12:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也快来换衣服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.36,0:12:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的要换衣服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.50,0:13:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.87,0:13:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呵呵呵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.71,0:13:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 我又出来了 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.64,0:13:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且上了镜只会傻笑 实在是很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.02,0:13:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我听紫吴说 你当上学生会长啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.05,0:13:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不容置疑地 这点是受到我这个哥哥的影响啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.49,0:13:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.69,0:13:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这个做弟弟的是看着哥哥的背影长大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.59,0:13:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都说不是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.33,0:13:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我不想变成你 所以才去当学生会长的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.34,0:13:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.54,0:13:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,实在是太深奥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.18,0:13:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像哥哥你这样的人 就是这样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.48,0:13:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像这间店对我来说是那么无法理解一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.35,0:13:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和哥哥的想法实在是差太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.72,0:14:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许我们基本上就不合吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.16,0:14:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 你这么说也有理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.13,0:14:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要那么明快的肯定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.67,0:14:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你千万别因此而受挫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.13,0:14:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,铁杵磨成绣花针 你要努力才行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.47,0:14:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥你也要努力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.44,0:14:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真没礼貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.17,0:14:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别看我这样 我可是个坚贞的努力家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.34,0:14:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像我这样不管做什么事都是孜孜不倦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.38,0:14:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 有时很细心 有时很大胆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.48,0:14:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,累积所有的努力才有现在的光荣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.82,0:14:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.92,0:14:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我到底该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.09,0:14:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.46,0:14:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.00,0:14:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我实在太高兴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.84,0:14:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘记你还在生我的气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.34,0:14:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,意随心动了起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.94,0:14:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想你不可能忘记吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.65,0:14:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,残酷的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.15,0:15:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对痛苦迟钝的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.79,0:15:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…第一次也是最后一次伸出的那双…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.33,0:15:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向我求救而伸出的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.90,0:15:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那双颤抖着的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.07,0:15:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我却轻易地甩开你的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.77,0:15:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那一幕你应该…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.17,0:15:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还没忘记吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.26,0:15:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,过去我对由希…既不喜欢也不讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.20,0:15:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是个"无"的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.67,0:15:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在我和由希再度重逢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.10,0:15:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一想到他可能会用同样的态度对我时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.74,0:15:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我第一次感到恐惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.62,0:16:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来不被人在乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.15,0:16:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是这么寂寞的一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.66,0:16:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我到现在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.70,0:16:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才了解这点已经太晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.90,0:16:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是由希…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.81,0:16:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的眼中却有看到我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.65,0:16:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也听到了我所说的话 而且为此生气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.72,0:16:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在他更坐在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.96,0:16:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打算来了解我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.39,0:16:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算我们两个不合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.10,0:16:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算我们个性不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.73,0:16:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又有什么关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.74,0:17:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.97,0:17:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们俩生出来时 我便带着你所没有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.71,0:17:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而你带着我所没有的东西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.15,0:17:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我觉得你所拥有的温柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.45,0:17:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是非常宝贵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.63,0:17:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且 由希你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.60,0:17:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对于我所拥有的无与伦比王家气质般的领袖风范
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.77,0:17:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也相当尊敬吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.50,0:17:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我了解 我了解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.57,0:17:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他到底是什么个性啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.55,0:17:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.12,0:17:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,店长 我有打扰到你们吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.85,0:17:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,服装换好了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.12,0:17:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点请她出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.29,0:18:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透小姐 快点出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.79,0:18:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点演下去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.13,0:18:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好看吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.14,0:18:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太美了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.74,0:18:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透果然是楚楚动人、白净无暇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.11,0:18:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最好是带条白色的狗、打着白色蕾丝边的洋伞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.84,0:18:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对 喝着红茶读着诗集
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.78,0:18:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐在饰着白色蕾丝窗帘的白色窗边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.58,0:18:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在干嘛 由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.22,0:18:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点称赞她几句吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.32,0:18:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托 拜托 小姐打扮得这么可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.02,0:18:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你实在太没礼貌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.76,0:19:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就由我来献上欢喜的一吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.03,0:19:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.19,0:19:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我被K了 哈…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.63,0:19:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是被他K啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.70,0:19:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到小透还真可爱 你的任务非常成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.51,0:19:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,值得我来加以赞扬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.27,0:19:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我深感光荣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.25,0:19:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,店长 你跟你弟弟是不是也有点进展了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.18,0:19:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗 我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.15,0:19:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.96,0:19:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许又是我独自…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.69,0:19:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在做着美梦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.48,0:19:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.22,0:20:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我总算了解哥哥一点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.25,0:20:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.12,0:20:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥他冗赘的言词和动作太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.76,0:20:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我没有心理准备的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.53,0:20:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只会被哥哥的步调给牵制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.23,0:20:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让自己陷于疲惫中罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.74,0:20:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说着说着我觉得好悲哀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.88,0:20:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.58,0:20:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很高兴今天能来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.02,0:20:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且 还看到了这么可爱的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.70,0:20:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是 这只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.98,0:21:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别遮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.25,0:21:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真浪漫啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.82,0:21:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才在你心中萌芽的感情就是男人的浪漫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.12,0:21:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男人果然是会因为一件衣服而动摇心智的生物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.49,0:21:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.16,0:21:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我了解 我了解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.16,0:21:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们就把美好的今天订为由希的浪漫纪念日…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.10,0:21:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,闭嘴！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.06,0:21:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,结果还是吵起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.17,0:21:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们就在旁边看着吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.31,0:21:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.05,0:21:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道后来怎么样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.75,0:21:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由于看到小透楚楚可怜的模样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.55,0:21:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以今天就变成由希的浪漫纪念日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.96,0:21:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟 你现在一定在想像小透穿那件洋装的样子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.99,0:21:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好坏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.03,0:21:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过也难怪啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.19,0:21:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是那种纯真无邪、牵着白狗打着白色洋伞…

